snippet.title: Louvre: The Final Curse/The Messenger - Game Trailer (2000)
snippet.description:
The Messenger - Game Trailer.
Developed by Arxel Tribe, index+, Réunion des Musées Nationaux.

Published in Europe by France Telecom Multimedia and Microids in 2000 for PC (Windows) and Playstation.
 Published in USA by DreamCatcher Interactive in 2001  for PC (Windows) and Macintosh

System : PC (Windows), Macintosh, Playstation.
Year : 2000/2001

Game Titles :
Louvre: L'Ultime Malédiction - France
Louvre: La maledizione finale - Italy
Louvre: La maldicion final - Spain
Louvre: A maldição - Portugal
Louvre: The Final Curse - UK
The Final Curse - Germany
The Messenger - North America


Trailer found on the couvermount CD of the french magazine PC Team (issue 53, April 2000)
